Product description

The Smart Home Alarm System is an ideal security solution for a wide range of settings, including residential homes, garages, warehouses, and garden sheds. Its versatile design and comprehensive components make it a reliable and effective tool for safeguarding your home.

Door/Window Magnetic Sensor

Remote control

Widely used

The minimum alarm sound is 120db.

SOS for emergency assistance

DIY Expansion

Cordless Door/Window Magnetic Sensor for Home Security Alarm Systems Kit. The optimal spacing between the magnetic strip and the door magnet should not exceed 1cm.

Press the arm key. Activates alarm if motion detector or door alarm triggered.

Press to disarm. Stops siren alarm.

You can place your wifi alarm security system in your home, shop, garage

The volume cannot be adjusted. The alarm duration can be adjusted on the APP (1-4 minutes).

The WiFi Alarm Home Security System kit can compatible with KERUI brand another type alarm hub,DIY complete alarm system as your need.

Suitable for indoor/outdoor

WiFi: Only connect with 2.4 G

Loud Alarm:120 dB

APP: Message timely notification

Control by remote or App

Note: Need to rearm after disarming to work

Infrared motion sensor

The motion sensor can detect 6 to 8 meters with a vertical angle of 60 degrees and a horizontal angle of 110 degrees.

Remote control

You can press the "S key" to immediately trigger an alarm. will need the "Bell key" to be pressed, makes a "didi-dididi" sound every time.

Wifi alarm security system Kit

When a sensor is triggered, the siren will sound immediately, it will continue to sound for approximately 2 minutes before stopping automatically.

    I got it connected to my router's 2.4 ghz network pretty fast. The remotes come with the batteries already active but the contact and motion sensors needed to be opened and physically connect the batteries. The app is very easy to navigate and I can program the alarm to arm and disarm by setting the specific times. No need to arm or disarm them manually every day. If alarm is activated it sends a signal to the phone and it rings on the phone. Perfect for a detached building. But the building needs to be withing the router’s 2.4 ghz network coverage.
